\\\"2.0\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"toolu_bdrk_012AqS59Ry4KPFCzn6i6qYa7\\\", \\\"result\\\": {\\\"content\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"text\\\": \\\"{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Agent specification created. Review and refine, then use deploy_agent to generate code.\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"spec\\\\\\\": {\\\\n    \\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Custom Agent\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Create a RemediationAgent that executes automated fixes for security incidents based on ForensicsAgent findings. It: 1) Reads the investigation report and recommended remediation, 2) For P2-P4 incidents, auto-executes predefined runbooks (restart deployments, scale services, rotate secrets), 3) For P1 incidents, requires human approval before executing, 4) Verifies the fix by checking system health post-remediation, 5) Links the executed runbook to the incident, 6) Resolves or escalates the incident based on outcome. Tools needed: runbook_quick_diagnostics, incident_resolve, incident_escalate, incident_link_runbook, incident_close, kubernetes_restart, kubernetes_scale. Framework: LangGraph StateGraph with human-in-the-loop interrupt for P1 incidents.\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"framework\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"langgraph\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"roles\\\\\\\": [\\\\n      {\\\\n        \\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"primary\\\\\\\",\\\\n        \\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Primary agent handling the main task\\\\\\\",\\\\n        \\\\\\\"goal\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Create a RemediationAgent that executes automated fixes for security incidents based on ForensicsAgent findings. It: 1) Reads the investigation report and recommended remediation, 2) For P2-P4 incidents, auto-executes predefined runbooks (restart deployments, scale services, rotate secrets), 3) For P1 incidents, requires human approval before executing, 4) Verifies the fix by checking system health post-remediation, 5) Links the executed runbook to the incident, 6) Resolves or escalates the incide